After some experimental checking, I have the ERV on low continuous, furnace fans on circulate and the radon exhauster on 2 hrs morning and 2 hours evening.  Radon now at about 2.0.  3,000 SF house air is much fresher and radon level is good - basement,  main level and upper master bedroom, all uniform at about 2.0.  I now have at our lake house.
